# It sets the frequency, amplitude, and phase of the output.
# The model is the medium through which the wave propagates.
#
# A vague prompt = low frequency = broad, diffuse output.
# A precise prompt = high frequency = sharp, specific output.
# A contradictory prompt = two frequencies at once = interference pattern.
